Enum SensorQuantity

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SensorQuantity>

    public enum SensorQuantity
extends java.lang.Enum<SensorQuantity>
    Defines Meterlink SensorQuantity data. This gives the information about sensor/channel measurement quantity.
